Here there is not much to explain, the idea is as follows:
Once you have installed the Office...


1) Run the "Microsoft_Toolkit_2.5.3.exe" file as an administrator !!!

2) Once you have opened, next to the progress bar, you'll find two buttons, touch the nearest (the "Office" symbol)

3) You go to the "Activation" tab, and touch on the green button that says: "EZ-Activator"

If all went well, you wait a few seconds and you'll have activated your Office.

I hope you have served.
Good Luck!
